<leg:heading inline="true"><desig><designum><refpt id="UCPN.UCPR.UCPRN05.R51-61.2" type="ext"/>(2)</designum></desig></leg:heading>
<leg:levelbody>
<leg:bodytext>
<p><text>An affidavit referred to in subrule (1)(b) must be filed as soon as practicable and, in any case, before the hearing date listed in the notice of motion that seeks the orders opposed.</text></p>
</leg:bodytext>
</leg:levelbody>
</leg:level-vrnt>
