<bodytext searchtype="COMMENTARY">
<p>
<text>An affidavit must be filed in support of, or in opposition to, a notice of motion. This rule overcomes the restriction which otherwise operates pursuant to 
<ci:cite searchtype="LEG-REF"><ci:content><remotelink dpsi="05CC" refpt="UCPN.SC.SCRC.PT35-9" remotekey1="REFPTID" service="DOC-ID" status="unval">UCPR r 35.9</remotelink></ci:content></ci:cite>
.</text></p>
</bodytext>
